# CopyButton

`TxCopyButton` copies a string to the clipboard and temporarily switches its label after success. It uses `navigator.clipboard.writeText` when available and falls back to a hidden textarea plus `document.execCommand('copy')`.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/copy-button/src/TxCopyButton.vue` and `copy-button.test.ts`.

